title: Test
summary: This is a multi-line chart with 2 lines representing Franchise, and Company-owned.
The line for Franchise has the highest values across Year with a mean value of 329.71,
and it peaked at 2017 with a value of 341.0.
Company-owned mostly had the least y-axis name with a mean value of 320.14,
which peaked at 2017 with a value of 385.0.
Company-owned reported the highest y-axis name  about 385.0 in Year 2017
Company-owned reported the lowest y-axis name  about 245.0 in Year 2011
Overall Company-owned is gradually increasing, Franchise is roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The difference of y_axis name between Franchise and Company-owned is smaller at Year 2017 compared to the Year 2011.
The greatest difference of y_axis name between Franchise and Company-owned occurs at Year 2011 and the smallest difference occurs at 2012.
